# =============================================================================
# School Booking API — Complete REST Client test file
# Extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao (VS Code)
# Click "Send Request" above any ### block to run it.
#
# WORKFLOW:
#   1. Run a token request → copy access_token → paste into @token below
#   2. Run requests top-to-bottom, copying IDs as you go
# =============================================================================


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VARIABLES  (fill in as you go)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@host         = http://localhost:3000
@kcUrl        = http://localhost:8081/realms/school_001/protocol/openid-connect/token

# Paste the access_token from a token request below:
@token        = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

# Paste IDs returned by create requests:
@schoolId     = PASTE_SCHOOL_ID_HERE
@teacherId    = PASTE_TEACHER_ID_HERE
@eventId      = PASTE_EVENT_ID_HERE
@slotId       = PASTE_SLOT_ID_HERE
@qrToken      = PASTE_QR_TOKEN_HERE

# Parent OTP flow:
@parentEmail  = parent@example.com
@otpCode      = PASTE_OTP_CODE_HERE
@parentToken  = PASTE_PARENT_TOKEN_HERE
@cancelToken  = PASTE_CANCEL_TOKEN_HERE


# =============================================================================
# 0. KEYCLOAK — GET TOKENS
# Run one of these, copy access_token → paste into @token above
# =============================================================================

### Token — platform_admin (full access)
POST {{kcUrl}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=school-portal&username=platform_admin&password=PlatformAdmin1234!

###

### Token — school_admin_1 (school-scoped admin)
POST {{kcUrl}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=school-portal&username=school_admin_1&password=Admin1234!

###

### Token — teacher_1 (read-only)
POST {{kcUrl}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=school-portal&username=teacher_1&password=Teacher1234!

###


# =============================================================================
# 1. HEALTH CHECK
# =============================================================================

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

###


# =============================================================================
# 2. SCHOOLS  (PLATFORM_ADMIN only for write, SCHOOL_ADMIN can read)
# =============================================================================

### Create school
# → Copy id from response → paste into @schoolId above
POST {{host}}/api/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Riverside Primary",
  "address": "12 River Rd, Springfield",
  "contactEmail": "admin@riverside.edu"
}

###

### List all schools
GET {{host}}/api/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get school by ID
GET {{host}}/api/schools/{{schoolId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update school (name, address, contactEmail, isActive)
PATCH {{host}}/api/schools/{{schoolId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Riverside Primary School",
  "address": "12 River Road, Springfield"
}

###

### Deactivate school (set isActive = false)
PATCH {{host}}/api/schools/{{schoolId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Delete school
# DELETE {{host}}/api/schools/{{schoolId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 3. TEACHERS  (SCHOOL_ADMIN write, SCHOOL_ADMIN + TEACHER read)
# =============================================================================

### Create teacher
# → Also creates a Keycloak user. Response includes tempPassword.
# → Copy id from response → paste into @teacherId above
POST {{host}}/api/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@riverside.edu",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "schoolId": "{{schoolId}}"
}

###

### List all teachers (scoped to school for SCHOOL_ADMIN)
GET {{host}}/api/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get teacher by ID
GET {{host}}/api/teachers/{{teacherId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update teacher (name, subject)
PATCH {{host}}/api/teachers/{{teacherId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane A. Smith",
  "subject": "Maths & Physics"
}

###

### Delete teacher (also removes Keycloak user)
# DELETE {{host}}/api/teachers/{{teacherId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 4. EVENTS  (SCHOOL_ADMIN write, SCHOOL_ADMIN + TEACHER read)
# =============================================================================

### Create event — SLOT_BOOKING (parent-teacher conferences)
# → Copy id from response → paste into @eventId above
# → Copy qrToken from response → paste into @qrToken above
POST {{host}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Parent-Teacher Conferences — Spring 2026",
  "description": "Spring term parent-teacher meetings",
  "eventType": "SLOT_BOOKING",
  "startDate": "2026-03-20T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-03-20T16:00:00.000Z",
  "location": "Main Hall",
  "schoolId": "{{schoolId}}"
}

###

### Create event — RSVP_SIGNUP (open day)
POST {{host}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Open Day 2026",
  "description": "Come see our school!",
  "eventType": "RSVP_SIGNUP",
  "startDate": "2026-04-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-04-01T14:00:00.000Z",
  "location": "School Grounds",
  "maxCapacity": 100,
  "schoolId": "{{schoolId}}"
}

###

### List all events (scoped to school)
GET {{host}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get event by ID (includes slots)
GET {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update event
PATCH {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Parent-Teacher Conferences — Spring 2026 (Updated)",
  "location": "Room 14"
}

###

### Delete event
# DELETE {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 5. SLOTS  (SCHOOL_ADMIN write, SCHOOL_ADMIN + TEACHER read)
# =============================================================================

### Create slots — bulk array (most common)
# → Copy a slot id from response → paste into @slotId above
POST {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "startTime": "2026-03-20T09:00:00.000Z",
    "endTime":   "2026-03-20T09:15:00.000Z",
    "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
    "maxBookings": 1
  },
  {
    "startTime": "2026-03-20T09:15:00.000Z",
    "endTime":   "2026-03-20T09:30:00.000Z",
    "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
    "maxBookings": 1
  },
  {
    "startTime": "2026-03-20T09:30:00.000Z",
    "endTime":   "2026-03-20T09:45:00.000Z",
    "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
    "maxBookings": 1
  },
  {
    "startTime": "2026-03-20T09:45:00.000Z",
    "endTime":   "2026-03-20T10:00:00.000Z",
    "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
    "maxBookings": 1
  }
]

###

### Create slot — single object
POST {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-03-20T10:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime":   "2026-03-20T10:15:00.000Z",
  "teacherId": "{{teacherId}}",
  "maxBookings": 2
}

###

### List slots for an event
GET {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update slot (change time or maxBookings)
PATCH {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxBookings": 2,
  "startTime": "2026-03-20T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime":   "2026-03-20T09:20:00.000Z"
}

###

### Delete slot
# DELETE {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 6. QR CODE  (SCHOOL_ADMIN only)
# The response is a PNG image — REST Client will display it inline.
# =============================================================================

### Get QR code PNG for event
# → Also note the qrToken printed in the terminal/response headers if needed
GET {{host}}/api/events/{{eventId}}/qr
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 7. PUBLIC ENDPOINTS — Event info via QR token (no auth)
# These are the endpoints the parent booking page calls after scanning QR.
# @qrToken comes from the event create response (field: qrToken)
# =============================================================================

### Get public event info by QR token
GET {{host}}/api/public/events/by-qr/{{qrToken}}

###

### Get public slots for event (includes available: true/false)
GET {{host}}/api/public/events/by-qr/{{qrToken}}/slots

###


# =============================================================================
# 8. OTP — PARENT AUTHENTICATION (no auth, public)
# Parents have no Keycloak account. They authenticate via email OTP.
# Check Mailhog at http://localhost:8025 for the OTP email.
# =============================================================================

### 8a. Send OTP to parent email
POST {{host}}/api/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{parentEmail}}",
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

###

### 8b. Verify OTP → returns parentToken (short-lived JWT)
# → Copy token from response → paste into @parentToken above
POST {{host}}/api/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{parentEmail}}",
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "code": "{{otpCode}}"
}

###


# =============================================================================
# 9. BOOKINGS — CREATE (parent token required)
# =============================================================================

### Book a slot — SLOT_BOOKING event
# → Copy cancelToken from response → paste into @cancelToken above
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{parentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": "{{slotId}}",
  "childName": "Alex Johnson"
}

###

### RSVP signup — RSVP_SIGNUP event (no slotId needed)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{parentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "childName": "Alex Johnson"
}

###


# =============================================================================
# 10. BOOKINGS — ADMIN VIEW (SCHOOL_ADMIN + TEACHER read)
# =============================================================================

### List all bookings (scoped to school's events)
GET {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter bookings by event
GET {{host}}/api/bookings?eventId={{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 11. BOOKINGS — CANCEL (public, no auth — link sent in confirmation email)
# =============================================================================

### View booking details by cancel token
GET {{host}}/api/bookings/{{cancelToken}}

###

### Cancel booking
DELETE {{host}}/api/bookings/{{cancelToken}}

###


# =============================================================================
# QUICK REFERENCE — All endpoints
# =============================================================================
#
#  Method  Path                                      Auth
#  ──────  ────────────────────────────────────────  ──────────────────────
#  GET     /health                                   none
#
#  POST    /api/schools                              PLATFORM_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/schools                              PLATFORM_ADMIN / SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/schools/:id                          PLATFORM_ADMIN / SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  PATCH   /api/schools/:id                          PLATFORM_ADMIN
#  DELETE  /api/schools/:id                          PLATFORM_ADMIN
#
#  POST    /api/teachers                             SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/teachers                             SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  GET     /api/teachers/:id                         SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  PATCH   /api/teachers/:id                         SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  DELETE  /api/teachers/:id                         SCHOOL_ADMIN
#
#  POST    /api/events                               SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/events                               SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  GET     /api/events/:id                           SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  PATCH   /api/events/:id                           SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  DELETE  /api/events/:id                           SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/events/:id/qr                        SCHOOL_ADMIN
#
#  POST    /api/events/:eventId/slots                SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  GET     /api/events/:eventId/slots                SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  PATCH   /api/slots/:id                            SCHOOL_ADMIN
#  DELETE  /api/slots/:id                            SCHOOL_ADMIN
#
#  GET     /api/public/events/by-qr/:qrToken         none (public)
#  GET     /api/public/events/by-qr/:qrToken/slots   none (public)
#
#  POST    /api/otp/send                             none (public)
#  POST    /api/otp/verify                           none (public)
#
#  POST    /api/bookings                             parent JWT
#  GET     /api/bookings                             SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  GET     /api/bookings?eventId=...                 SCHOOL_ADMIN / TEACHER
#  GET     /api/bookings/:cancelToken                none (public)
#  DELETE  /api/bookings/:cancelToken                none (public)
#
# =============================================================================
